            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "萬科發布業績預警 預計2025年虧損擴大至820億元人民幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 萬科表示，預計2025年虧損額擴大三分之二，原因包括房地產開發項目結算規模顯著下降等。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五，提交給香港交易所的業績預告顯示，萬科預計全年虧損約820億元人民幣 （約合118億美元），上年同期虧損495億元人民幣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Vanke Warns 2025 Loss May Have Widened to $11.8 Billion</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%90%AC%E7%A7%91%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E6%A5%AD%E7%B8%BE%E9%A0%90%E8%AD%A6-%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%882025%E5%B9%B4%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%B3820%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3-131445953.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-30 22:18:30",
